<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA526_07_SU_0004_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    
    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />
    
    <!-- 개별 -->
    <script src="./../../common_contents/js/ema526_07_0004.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema526_07.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema526_07_su_0004">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="2_orange" lang="y">동전을 한 개 던질 때 일이 일어날 가능성을 수로 나타내어 봅시다.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents paging_layout">
        <article class="page page_1">
          <h3 lang="y">그림면이 나올 가능성을 수로 나타내어 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="flex">
            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA526_07_SU/0004_content.png" alt="">

            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <button data-answer-single="true">
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>2</span>
                </div>
              </button>
              <button data-answer-single="false">
                <span>0</span>
              </button>
              <button data-answer-single="false">
                <span>1</span>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="page page_2">
          <h3 lang="y">숫자면이 나올 가능성을 수로 나타내어 보세요.</h3>

          <div class="flex">
            <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA526_07_SU/0004_content.png" alt="">

            <div class="boolean_wrap">
              <button data-answer-single="true">
                <div class="fraction_box">
                  <span>1</span>
                  <span>2</span>
                </div>
              </button>
              <button data-answer-single="false">
                <span>0</span>
              </button>
              <button data-answer-single="false">
                <span>1</span>
              </button>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
